'''Maciej Popowicz''' (born 1984) – creator of [[nasza-klasa.pl]], the [[Poland|Polish]] version of [[social networking site]] [[Classmates.com]] and student of [[computer science]] at [[University of Wrocław]]. He became one of the youngest Polish millionaires, after he sold 20% of shares of nasza-klasa.pl (20,000,000 zlotys, about $6,300,000, €4,500,000, £3,850,000) to German [[venture capital]] fund, ''European Founders'' in 2007.<ref>[http://manager.money.pl/ludzie/portrety/artykul/wroclawski;student;milionerem,13,0,266253.html Maciej Popowicz, founder of Nasza-klasa.pl]</ref> In 2008 [[Estonia]]n fund ''Forticom'' bought 70% of shares of nasza-klasa.pl, with estimated worth 175,000,000 zlotys (about $55,000,000, €39,000,000, £34,000,000). In 2007 he got the ''Człowiek Roku Polskiego Internetu'' (''Person of the Year of Polish Internet'') prize.

